Guidelime.registerGuide(
[[
[N44-45 Tanaris]
[GA Horde]
[D A guide created by T H A C E N#9446\Based on Joana's Speed Leveling guide https://www.joanasworld.com]
01) As you enter Gadgetzan (next to the crane, [G52,27Tanaris]) turn in "[QT2864 Tran'Rek]" ([G52,27]), SKIP "Scarab Shells" (Dungeon).
02) From the Wanted Poster next to the cage entrance ([G52,27]), accept "[QA2781 WANTED: Caliph Scorpidsting]" and "[QA2875 WANTED: Andre Firebeard]".
03) Go in the Inn on the east side and make Gadgetzan your new home from the Innkeeper ([G52,28]).
04) Next to the Inn at the windmill (just south, [G52,29]), accept "[QA1707 Water Pouch Bounty]" and "[QA1690 Wastewander Justice]".
05) At the Bank next to you, get the following items out: Goblin Rumors and Seaforium Booster. Put in the bank: Deepstrider Tumor.
06) At the western side of Gadgetzan on top of the hill, accept "[QA992 Gadgetzan Water Survey]" ([G50,28]).
07) Go north to the Shimmering Flats at the Mirage Raceway and from the dwarf turn in "[QT1117 Rumors for Kravel]" ([G78,77] in Thousand Needles). Wait a few seconds, then accept "[QA1118 Back to Booty Bay]".
08) Next to you from the gnome, turn in "[QT1137 News for Fizzle]" ([G78,77]).
09) Go over to the goblin's side of the Mirage Raceway and turn in "[QT1187 Razzeric's Tweaking]" ([G80,76]), accept "[QA1188 Safety First]". Next to you, accept "[QA1190 Keeping Pace]".
10) At the goblin Zamek /target next to the Goblin Racer, click on Complete Quest to setup a distraction, then go in the gnome's hut and click on Rizzle's Unguarded Plans ([G77,77]) to turn in "[QT1190 Keeping Pace]", accept "[QA1194 Rizzle's Schematics]".
11) Go to the goblin Pozzik and turn in "[QT1194 Rizzle's Schematics]" ([G80,76]).
12) Hearth (or run back) to Gadgetzan. NOTE: You can now destroy the Sample of Indurium Ore as it is no longer used for anything.
13) From Shreev at the western side of Gadgetzan, turn in "[QT1188 Safety First]" ([G51,27]), SKIP the next part.
14) Grind your way east to the Noonshade Ruins (around [G60,24]) and start working on "[QC1690 Wastewander Justice]" along with "[QC1707 Water Pouch Bounty]": kill/loot the Wastewander humans. NOTES: Do not sell the Wastewander Water Pouches to a vendor! Just clear the area once and continue on...
15) Go east to Steamwheedle Port and from the female goblin under the red tent, accept "[QA8365 Pirate Hats Ahoy!]" ([G67,22]).
16) From the male troll under the green tent, accept "[QA3520 Screecher Spirits]" ([G67,22]). 
17) At the other side of the Port, in the hut ([G67,24]), turn in "[QT2872 Stoley's Debt]", accept "[QA2873 Stoley's Shipment]". And next to you, accept "[QA8366 Southsea Shakedown]".
18) Go SW to the Waterspring Field (around [G64,30]) and finish "[QC1690 Wastewander Justice]" along with "[QC1707 Water Pouch Bounty]": kill/loot the needed Wastewander mobs. Also, keep an eye out for Caliph Scorpidsting /target, he patrols around the area and has 2 rogues following him. This is for "[QC2781 WANTED: Caliph Scorpidsting]", and you will have another opportunity later to do this if you cannot find him now.
19) Go to Lost Rigger Cove (entrance at [G69,41])...
20) Start working on "[QC8366 Southsea Shakedown]" along with "[QC8365 Pirate Hats Ahoy!]": kill/loot the Southsea humans (the Southsea Dock Workers are up at [G75,48]). Any of these mobs has a chance to drop a Pirate's footlocker, which could contain an item which starts "[QA2876 Ship Schedules]", accept it if you are able to find it, if not at least grind for awhile as it might show up, otherwise it can be skipped. While doing this, also go do the following 2 steps below in this same area:
21) "[QC2873 Stoley's Shipment]": loot the Stolen Cargo up in the building ([G72,47]).
22) "[QC2875 WANTED: Andre Firebeard]": kill/loot Andre Firebeard /target in the middle of the cove ([G73,47]). Watch out this fight usually involves 3 adds. (See Video).
23) Once all these are done (including "[QC8366 Southsea Shakedown]" along with "[QC8365 Pirate Hats Ahoy!]"), then hearth to Gadgetzan. Make sure you are repaired/resupplied.
24) Next to the Inn at the windmill ([G52,29]), turn in "[QT1707 Water Pouch Bounty]" and "[QT1690 Wastewander Justice]", accept "[QA1691 More Wastewander Justice]".
25) Grind west to Sandsorrow Watch and do "[QC992 Gadgetzan Water Survey]": use the Untapped Dowsing Widget quest item in the pool ([G39,29]). Watch out, as soon as you fill the widget, a few high level bugs will spawn. Either run away or try to kill them.
26) Grind back east to Gadgetzan and on top of the hill, turn in "[QT992 Gadgetzan Water Survey]" ([G50,28]), SKIP "Noxious Lair Investigation" (for now).
27) Grind east to Steamwheedle Port and from the female goblin under the red tent, turn in "[QT8365 Pirate Hats Ahoy!]" ([G67,22]). Then you can get resupplied in the hut next to you.
28) At the other side of the Port, in the hut ([G67,24]), turn in "[QT2873 Stoley's Shipment]", accept "[QA2874 Deliver to MacKinley]". Next to you, turn in "[QT2875 WANTED: Andre Firebeard]", "[QT8366 Southsea Shakedown]" and (if you have it) "[QT2876 Ship Schedules]".
29) Go SW to the Waterspring Field (around [G60,38]) and do "[QC1691 More Wastewander Justice]" along with (if you still need to) "[QC2781 WANTED: Caliph Scorpidsting]": kill the needed Wastewander humans and kill/loot Caliph Scorpidsting /target, he patrols around the area and has 2 rogues following him.
30) Hearth (or run back) to Gadgetzan and at the windmill next to the Inn ([G52,29], #1 on map), turn in "[QT1691 More Wastewander Justice]" and "[QT2781 WANTED: Caliph Scorpidsting]".
31) Go into the Bank next to you ([G52,29]) and put into it: Kravel's Scheme, Stoley's Bottle, any Wastewander Water Pouches and if you have found the item called OOX-17/TN Distress Beacon, put that in your bank as well (and don't accept the quest from it yet).
32) Go to the Wind Rider Master (north of Gadgetzan, [G52,25]) and fly to Freewind Post, Thousand Needles. 
33) Go west into Feralas...
[NX 45-46 Feralas]
]], "Thacen")
